<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>404 Not Found</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6e8efb, #a777e3);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    .error-code {
      font-size: 10rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6ec4, #7873f5);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .home-btn {
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #6e8efb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: 0.3s;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    .home-btn:hover {
      background: #6e8efb;
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="error-code">404</div>
    <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
    <p>We can't seem to find the page you're looking for. Go back home and continue exploring!</p>
    <a href="/" class="home-btn">back</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
